import {FloatingLabel, Form} from 'react-bootstrap'

export const FloatingLabelsEmail = (props) => {

   return <>

        <FloatingLabel
            controlId="floatingInput"
            label="Email address"
            className="mb-3"
        >

            <Form.Control 
                type="email" 
                name="email"
                placeholder="name@example.com" 
                value = {this.props.val}
                onChange={()=> this.props.handleChange()}
            />

        </FloatingLabel>

    </>
}
